theorem ContinuousLinearEquiv.homothety_inverse (a : exprℝ) (ha : 0 < a) (f : «expr ≃ₛₗ[ ] » E σ F) :

  rw [← mul_assoc, inv_mul_cancel (ne_of_lt ha).symm, one_mul]
